                        </svg>
                        Page Information (Auto-detected)
                    </h4>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
                        <div>
                            <label class="block text-gray-600 font-medium">Current Page:</label>
